{"tid":1845917,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［有法必依］將起訴違法武漢病人加入訴求之一","createTime":"2020-01-27T11:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T10:53:34.000Z","uid":67356,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d3add0600b280b61f472648cdd8e6512b06530c9","tid":1845917,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/liar-18_kTVoC_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fliar-18_kTVoC_1200x0.png&h=041ccd6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第599A章 《預防及控制疾病規例》<br />\n8.旅客應衞生主任要求提供資料<br />\n(1)為預防任何傳染病或污染的發生，或防止任何傳染病或污染的蔓延，衞生主任可要求旅客向該衞生主任提供他所要求的任何資料。<br />\n(2)旅客須遵從根據第(1)款提出的要求。<br />\n(3)任何人違反第(2)款，或明知而向衞生主任提供任何在要項上屬虛假的資料，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁6個月。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3913707/org/4c78e455db24b95e6d5345ef092d0119.jpg/N4piAyXSXh7oKezUzaFKaBmlFZVtdnXcQT8i70E_Iu8?v=w1120r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3913707%2Forg%2F4c78e455db24b95e6d5345ef092d0119.jpg%2FN4piAyXSXh7oKezUzaFKaBmlFZVtdnXcQT8i70E_Iu8%3Fv%3Dw1120r16_9&h=a026dca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n29.出入限制<br />\n(1)任何人不得離開該人被檢疫或隔離所在的地方。<br />\n(2)除衞生主任外，任何人不得在未獲根據第31條給予的書面准許下 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n          (a)進入另一人被檢疫或隔離所在的地方；或<br />\n          (b)進入或離開受隔離的地方。<br />\n(3)任何人違反第(1)或(2)款，即屬犯罪，一經定罪，可處第2級罰款及監禁6個月。<br />\n<br />\n如果律政司放生違法病人即係鼓勵大陸人嚟香港散播病毒，律政司漠視香港醫護人員生命安危<br />\n咁樣醫護唔罷工都唔得喇"},{"pid":"4f8be4f540af585324b51c3bab5e866f138621b3","tid":1845917,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:43:48.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ab243aefc86f4f821d5fb058488a9e9f7bedd6","tid":1845917,"uid":176999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:44:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"665beb5710ad56de73eca45790